original: Johanson, John Ingvar, tandläkare, Borås, f. 17/12/08 i Borås av gross-handl. Albert J. o. Adelina Svensson. G. 41 m. Karin Hjelm. Barn: Kristina f. 41, Per 44. — Stud:ex. i Borås 27, tandhkand. 29, tandl. 32. Tandl. v. Borås ’skoltandpoliklinik 33-45, priv:prakt. i Borås ised. 46.
translated: Johanson, John Ingvar, dentist, Borås, b. 17/12/08 in Borås to grocer Albert J. and Adelina Svensson. Married in 1941 to Karin Hjelm. Children: Kristina b. 1941, Per b. 1944. He passed his studentexamen in Borås in 1927, graduated from dental school in 1929, and became a licensed dentist in 1932. He worked at the school dental clinic in Borås from 1933-1945, and had a private practice in Borås starting in 1946.
